{"tid":1038706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報道:滙控調查引致孟晚舟案曝光","createTime":"2019-02-27T01:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T01:12:53.000Z","uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad667a6465404e483571929db06a1cb25714180","tid":1038706,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"路透引述文件稱，中國電訊業巨擘華為副董事長兼財務總監孟晚舟被捕，是源自滙豐控股(00005)的一宗內部調查所揭發。<br />\n<br />\n根據文件顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>滙控在2016年為了取悅美國司法部，避免被起訴違反美國禁令，因此進行內部調查，最終發現華為與一間早已出售的公司有密切關連，以及出售電訊產品予伊朗的證據。有關調查發現是司法部現正提出引渡孟晚舟回美國受審的重要佐證</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n華為拒評上述消息。滙控發言人回應稱，該銀行不是調查對象。司法部拒評上述消息。"},{"pid":"5eb99654fa14c3a8d5ab1d3f6c642e646d84276e","tid":1038706,"uid":107231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:02:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱出獄？"},{"pid":"b8b24106bc40f49393ec3ba9b17ac595520cacbe","tid":1038706,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eb99654fa14c3a8d5ab1d3f6c642e646d84276e","tid":1038706,"uid":107231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:02:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱出獄？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2067977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2067977&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6Uv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=ad26aecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2067977</a><br />\n<br />\n俾埋條Link你拎去同信報講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49481a72dc496d231e140793cc980dcb529a5e40","tid":1038706,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:05:50.000Z","msg":"匯豐咁聽美國佬話<br />\n信之不得<br />\n<br />\n配合大灣區<br />\n香港當取替 外國勢力金融機構<br />\n<br />\n用中資金融機構<br />\n全面控制港幣利息、發鈔等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e5cd34136e96ec70c1b7ff79d77adee62bc46a","tid":1038706,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8b24106bc40f49393ec3ba9b17ac595520cacbe","tid":1038706,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eb99654fa14c3a8d5ab1d3f6c642e646d84276e","tid":1038706,"uid":107231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:02:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱出獄？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2067977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2067977&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6Uv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=ad26aecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2067977</a><br />\n<br />\n俾埋條Link你拎去同信報講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"華為孟晚舟被舉報 滙豐戶口有可疑交易<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2018-12-08</span></span></strong>港聞 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  （星島日報報道）中美恢復貿易談判之際，內地科技巨頭華為集團副董事長兼首席財務官孟晚舟在加拿大被捕，美國要求將她引渡，香港時間今天凌晨出席在溫哥華法庭召開的保釋聆訊。據悉，孟晚舟被捕，是美國調查她涉嫌利用滙豐銀行逃避美國對伊朗制裁，滙豐的聯邦任命監督機構向檢方舉報華為帳戶存在可疑交易。美國國安顧問波頓證實，他事先知情拘捕行動。至於中美元首在晚宴之前是否知道，媒體眾說紛紜。<br />\n<br />\n  華為創始人任正非的女兒孟晚舟本月一日（即中美元首會晤當天）因被控違反美國對伊朗的出口禁令，在加拿大轉機被捕。消息一出震撼全球股市，投資人擔心美中貿易戰升級。《華爾街日報》形容，這標誌着中美科技交鋒進入更激烈的階段，也將進一步促使美國盟友與華為劃清界線。<br />\n<br />\n  加拿大司法部稱是應美國要求採取行動，並可能引渡她到美國，香港時間今天淩晨在溫哥華法庭舉行保釋聆訊。溫哥華的移民法律師Richard Kurland稱，「你需要大量資料及證據才能支持拘留釋放」。他表示如果對保釋沒有做出裁決，孟晚舟料將續被拘留。<br />\n<br />\n  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">路透社報道</span>，孟晚舟被捕，是美國調查她涉嫌利用全球銀行體系逃避美國對伊朗制裁的一環。至少自二○一六年起，美國便一直在調查華為是否違反美國對伊朗的制裁，最近的調查包括華為利用匯豐控股進行相關的非法交易。</span><br />\n<br />\n  匯豐二○一二年支付十九點二億美元，與布魯克林（Brooklyn）聯邦檢察署就違反美國制裁和洗錢法達成一項延後起訴協議。《華爾街日報》引述消息人士說，負責評估匯豐近幾年反洗錢和制裁管理辦法的外部監督機構Exiger，向紐約東區聯邦檢方提交與華為交易有關的資訊。<br />\n<br />\nReuters 自己都報過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526d388386945e4df33ede08b073dcc1aedffaba","tid":1038706,"uid":116989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8b24106bc40f49393ec3ba9b17ac595520cacbe","tid":1038706,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eb99654fa14c3a8d5ab1d3f6c642e646d84276e","tid":1038706,"uid":107231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:02:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱出獄？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2067977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2067977&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6Uv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=ad26aecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2067977</a><br />\n<br />\n俾埋條Link你拎去同信報講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:11:35.000Z","msg":"二樓係串d，但呢單野好似舊年拉人時已經有報道過，可能外電炒多次詳細版，信報又無為意"},{"pid":"5bee633270a1030d2429c7a3c71dc608edf10694","tid":1038706,"uid":107231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8b24106bc40f49393ec3ba9b17ac595520cacbe","tid":1038706,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eb99654fa14c3a8d5ab1d3f6c642e646d84276e","tid":1038706,"uid":107231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:02:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱出獄？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2067977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2067977&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6Uv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=ad26aecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2067977</a><br />\n<br />\n俾埋條Link你拎去同信報講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181210/59012597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181210%2F59012597&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6Uv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=478c1acc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181210%2F59012597&h=a61d2e2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181210/59012597</a><br />\n睇多啲新聞啦"}]}